{"type":"message","id":"5e486f0c","parentId":"c825787f","timestamp":"2026-03-14T02:29:14.581Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now update MEMORY.md with the new info.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"f95f0d0d-bc94-4a75-a891-9ab7afb6309e","name":"edit","arguments":{"new_string":"## Browser Automation — agent-browser\n\n**Status:** ✅ v0.20.0 | Chrome 146 installed | `--no-sandbox` set in `~/.agent-browser/config.json`\n\n```bash\nagent-browser open <url>              # Navigate\nagent-browser snapshot -i             # Interactive tree with refs (@e1, @e2, ...)\nagent-browser click @e2 / fill @e3 \"text\"  # Interact by ref\nagent-browser screenshot [path]       # Screenshot\nagent-browser eval \"document.title\"   # Run JS\nagent-browser get title / url / text @ref  # Query page\nagent-browser close                   # Done\n```\n\n**Config:** `~/.agent-browser/config.json` has `{\"args\": \"--no-sandbox\"}` (Ubuntu AppArmor requirement)\n**Howto:** `/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/Agent-Browser-howto.md`\n**Notes:** Prefer `snapshot -i` with refs over CSS selectors. Daemon auto-starts. Chrome at `~/.agent-browser/browsers/`.","old_string":"## Browser Automation — agent-browser\n\n**Status:** ✅ Installed & working (v0.19.0) | Symlink fix: v1200→v1208\n\n```bash\nagent-browser open <url>              # Navigate\nagent-browser snapshot -i             # Interactive tree with refs (@e1, @e2, ...)\nagent-browser click @e2 / fill @e3 \"text\"  # Interact by ref\nagent-browser screenshot [path]       # Screenshot\nagent-browser eval \"document.title\"   # Run JS\nagent-browser close                   # Done\n```\n\n**Howto:** `/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/Agent-Browser-howto.md`\n**Notes:** Daemon auto-starts. Chromium symlinked at `~/.cache/ms-playwright/chromium_headless_shell-1200 → -1208`. Prefer `snapshot -i` with refs over CSS selectors — more reliable for AI.","path":"/home/pete/.openclaw/workspace/MEM