{"type":"message","id":"49903f85","parentId":"1556b11f","timestamp":"2026-03-14T11:10:24.178Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Memory updated with all the new Chrome insights and gotchas.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Done. MEMORY.md now has:\n\n- **Both browser systems** documented (agent-browser CLI + OpenClaw built-in)\n- **All three profiles** with their use cases (`openclaw`, `user`, `chrome-relay`)\n- **The `DevToolsActivePort` gotcha** with the manual creation workaround\n- **Port binding gotcha** when multiple Chrome instances share a user-data-dir\n- **`chrome://` URL blocking** noted\n- **New 2026.3.13 features** (batched actions, hardened lifecycle, shared ARIA roles)\n- **Quick reference** for both tools\n\nDaily notes updated too. Next time I need a browser, I'll know exactly which tool to reach for and what landmines to avoid."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/hunter-alpha","usage":{"input":627,"output":194,"cacheRead":207424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":208245,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773486613767}}
